# textdomain: vl_tridents
Trident=Trizob
Water element=Vodni element

Tridents are great in melee combat, as they have an increased reach. They can also be thrown.=Trizobi so odlični v boju od blizu, saj imajo povečan doseg. Lahko se jih tudi vrže.

To throw a trident, hold it in your hand, then hold use (rightclick) in the air.=Če želite vreči trizob, ga držite v roki in nato pridržite tipko za uporabo (desni klik) v zraku.